<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.6">
<l>cittirakū ṭattiruppac ciṟukākkai mulaitīṇṭa</l>
<l>vattiramē koṇṭeṟiya vaṉaittulakun tirintōṭi</l>
<l>vittakaṉē yirāmāvō niṉṉapaya meṉṟaḻaippa</l>
<l>vattiramē yataṉkaṇṇai yaṟuttatumō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While sitting on Cittirakūṭa,</l>
<l rend="indent">a little crow touched [your] breast,</l>
<l>so [you] discharged a missile</l>
<l rend="indent">[which] ran chasing [it] throughout the world</l>
<l>until [it] cried out,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Wise One! Oh Rāmā! [Please give] your refuge!”</l>
<l>and that missile pierced [its] eye.</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
